
OpenDocument Thumbnail Creator
================================

KDE thumbnail-plugin that generates small images (thumbnails)
for ODF (OpenDocument Format) files, to be displayed, for example,
on Konqueror and Dolphin file managers.


DEPENDENCIES
`````````````
The following libraries and development packages are needed:
KDE Frameworks >=5.0.x
QT             >=5.2.x


INSTALLATION
`````````````
     mkdir build
     cd build
     cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=`kf5-config --prefix` ..         <- DON'T forget ..
     make
     su -c 'make install'
     kbuildsycoca5 (optional)

No conflict exists with the kde4 based thumbnail plugins for KOffice and LibreOffice/OpenOffice. 
If these are ever ported they are to be prefered.

